data.description: Perfect starter home in this small, friendly Lake Sawyer area community! Situated on one of the largest lots in the neighborhood, this 1600SF, 3 bed, 2.5 bath home will check all of the necessary boxes. Cozy gas stove in living room will keep you toasty warm through the cold winter weather and ceiling fans will help circulate the heat. Laundry conveniently located upstairs. Walking distance to Lake Sawyer and just across the street from Lake Sawyer Market. New roof with 50 transferable warranty, new stainless steel kitchen appliances, new covered patio pavers, new storage shed with gravel utility area!
